ctive little vessel that can be used for any type of hot or cold liquid - but it designed to be used specifically with Hario V60 brewers. The brewer simply rests on top of the heat resistant decanter and as you pour, it will slowly fill with delicious coffee. You can then decant as you require.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDishwasher Safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMicrowave Safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCapacity: 400ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeatproof Glass\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade in Japan\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"visibility: hidden;\"\u003ecarafes hari hair haro hario pour ove v60 hairio v60 02 hair v60 02\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":12292662689875,"sku":"HCD-2T","price":19.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hcd-2t-resize.jpg?v=1525727415"},{"product_id":"hario-v60-03-coffee-server","title":"Hario V60-03 Coffee Server","description":"\u003cp\u003eYou want a great value server that wouldn't look out of place in a retro diner? Well this little fella is your man! To keep the server sealed, it comes with a black plastic lid that keeps heat in and prevent spills, and it has a 1 litre functional capacity; enough to hold coffee warmly for 3-4 people.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePractical Capacity: 1000ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeatproof Glass\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePolypropylene Lid and Handle\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSilicone Rubber Seal\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMicrowave Safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDishwasher Safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade in Japan\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":27854193492051,"sku":"VCS-03B","price":18.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/vcs-03b-edit.jpg?v=1556058478"},{"product_id":"hario-v60-03-insulated-stainless-steel-server-white","title":"Hario V60-03 Insulated Stainless Steel Server White","description":"\u003cp\u003eYou're hard at work, fuelled only by delicious coffee that you brewed to keep you on point. Suddenly, you go to take a drink but your cup is empty so you pick up your decanter to refill your cup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut disaster! The coffee has gone cold!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConcentration broken, you have to break away to brew more, only to never recover your train of thought. However, that was a 2016 problem.\u003c\/p\u003e\nIn 2017, Hario has introduced an insulated stainless steel coffee server with a super sleek modern design.\n\u003cp\u003eThis 750ml, vacuum sealed, double wall beauty will allow you to serve, and enjoy, your favourite coffee for longer, ensuring your concentration never need be broken.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou can even brew directly in to the carafe from your beloved V60 dripper.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePractical Capacity: 750ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDual Wall Stainless Steel Body\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePolypropylene Spout, Handle and Lid\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eABS Resin Lever\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSilicone Gasket\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade in China\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCleaning the Server's Exterior:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoak a soft cloth in water with dish detergent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWring out the cloth firmly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWipe off any stains\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDry with a soft cloth\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not use steel scrub brushes, etc.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCleaning the Lid:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRemove the seal\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWash the lid with a soft sponge that has soaked in hot water with dish detergent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRinse thoroughly in clean water until no detergent remains\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDry with a soft cloth\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCleaning the Server's Interior:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWash with a long-handled sponge that has soaked in hot water with dish detergent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRinse thoroughly in clean water until no detergent remains\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDry thoroughly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAn odour may occur if a drink or residue remains inside for a prolonged period, if this occurs, clean with an enzyme-based bleach before rinsing thoroughly and allowing it to dry completely with the lid off\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"visibility: hidden;\"\u003eV60 carafe decanter dewar flask thermos thermal insulation insulate doublewall double-wall large \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":38055498547389,"sku":"VHS-80W","price":79.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/vhs-80w-1.jpg?v=1612631550"},{"product_id":"hario-beaker-server-300ml","title":"Hario Beaker Server (300ml)","description":"\u003cp\u003eNo need to rest your chemistry!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven without Dr. Honeydew, you can still bring the lab home with this beaker to serve your coffee.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe wide, flat handle is easy to grip for a steady, controlled pour. The guide marks also make it a great measuring cup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCapacity: 300 ml (10.14 oz)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWidth: 125 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDepth: 89 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeight: 105 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeatproof glass\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTop-rack dishwasher safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMicrowave safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade in Japan\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"display: none;\"\u003ebeakers hari hair cone hairo lab beeker chemistry\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":40483856416957,"sku":"BV-300","price":27.5,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_beaker_server_300.jpg?v=1629398588"},{"product_id":"hario-beaker-server-600ml","title":"Hario Beaker Server (600ml)","description":"\u003cp\u003eMake more chemistry with more people!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhen your coffee experiments involve two (or more) people, make sure you have enough to give everyone a taste.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith a substantial 600 ml capacity and a wide, flat handle so you don't lose your grip, this big beaker will help maintain a steady, controlled pour. The guide marks also make it a great measuring cup.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCapacity: 600 ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWidth: 130 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDepth: 90 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeight: 152 mm\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emade in Japan from heatproof glass\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003etop-rack dishwasher safe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"display: none;\"\u003ebeakers hari hair cone hairo lab beeker chemistry\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":40484043489469,"sku":"BV-600","price":36.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_beaker_server_600.jpg?v=1629398794"}],"url":"https:\/\/www.hario-canada.ca\/collections\/servers.oembed","provider":"Hario Canada","version":"1.0","type":"link"}